    {"@type":"Question","name":"How do I build trust in the mortgage business?","acceptedAnswer":{"@type":"Answer","text":"Trust is built through transparency, responsiveness, doing what you say, and putting the client's interest first — consistently. In a high-stakes financial decision, people refer the originator who made them feel informed and safe. Trust is the foundation that all mortgage marketing rests on."}},
