        </div>
        <div class="body-text">
          <p>Here's the truth most mortgage training skips: the licensing covered in <a class="inline-link" href="/mortgage-career/mortgage-license/">how to get a mortgage license</a> gets you in the door, but mortgage marketing is what determines whether you build a career or fade out. The single biggest reason new loan officers fail isn't the exam &mdash; it's that they never learn to generate business.</p>
